    "description": [
      "One of the neighboring longhouses sits atop a tiered hillock ringed with concentric stones.  Braziers encircle the base of the hill, blazing bright in the aurora-lit gloom and filling the air with the huskiness of musky incense.  The crushed stones of the path rise laboriously toward a monstrous hoarbeam tree that dominates the skyline to the north, lanterns glimmering in its ancient branches."
